title: BROUSKO 133
description:
BROUSKO EPISODIO 133 DVD RIP

Perilipsi:

O Shfhs anastatwnetai poly me thn anavolh tou xeirourgeiou kai h Anastasia me ton Antwnh prospathoyn na ton kathhsyxasoun. O Nektarios ta vazei me ta aderfia tou kai th giagia, kathgorwntas tous oti tou apokryptoun plhrofories gia thn yiothesia tou. H Dhmhtra, ton kathhsyxazei kai me afth thn aformh erxontai pio konta sthn epanasyndesh, gegonos pou tha eksorgisei th Xristina kai tha kanei ston Nektario mia anev prohgoumenou epithesh. O Diamanths einai tromera provlhmatismenos kai anhsyxos apo thn apokalypsh tou Nektariou sxetika me to poia einai h viologikh tou mhtera. H Melina, se kakh psyxologikh katastash, eksomologeitai ston Axillea to poso th varainei to thema ths apokthshs enos paidioy. O Markos kanei protash gamou sth Dafnh alla h apanthsh ths tha ton ekplhksei.
